                                 H.E.L.P

[add + fileName; a] add a file
[edit + fileName; e] edit/add a file
[list; l] list files
[delete + fileName; d] remove a file
[search + wordName; s] search globaly a word
[search + wordName + -r title/project/context; s] search a word
[view + fileName; v] view a file
[help;h] help
[quit;q] quit

[configuration] config.xml

[*] Notes should not have suffix for being able to be transformed.

